{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Storage","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Storage","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Storage_API\">Web Storage API <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Storage\"><code>Storage</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Storage/length\"><code>length</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methods</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Storage/clear\"><code>clear()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Storage/getItem\"><code>getItem()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Storage/key\"><code>key()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Storage/removeItem\"><code>removeItem()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Storage/setItem\"><code>setItem()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Web Storage API</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StorageEvent\"><code>StorageEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Window/localStorage\"><code>Window.localStorage</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Window/sessionStorage\"><code>Window.sessionStorage</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Storage_API\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Web Storage API (en-US)</a> 中的 <strong><code>Storage</code></strong> 介面提供了存取特定 domain session 及本機儲存的方法。舉例而言，它能夠對存取的資料進行新增、刪除、修改，</p>\n<p>在操作上，如果是對象是 domain session storage ，會呼叫 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Window/sessionStorage\"><code>Window.sessionStorage</code></a> 。而若是 local storage，則呼叫 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Window/localStorage\"><code>Window.localStorage</code></a> 。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"屬性","title":"屬性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"storage.length_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Storage/length\"><code>Storage.length</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>返回一數字，代表儲存在 <code>Storage</code> 中的物件的數量。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"方法","title":"方法","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"storage.key_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Storage/key\"><code>Storage.key()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>當傳入一數字 <code>n</code>, 會返回 storage 裡第 n 個值的 key 值。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"storage.getitem_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Storage/getItem\"><code>Storage.getItem()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>當傳入一 key 值, 會返回 storage 裡此 key 值對應的 value 。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"storage.setitem_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Storage/setItem\"><code>Storage.setItem()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>當傳入 key 及 value 的值, 會在 storage 裡新增此 key 及 value 值，若 key 已存在，則會把值更新成傳入的 value。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"storage.removeitem_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Storage/removeItem\"><code>Storage.removeItem()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>當傳入一 key 值, 會把此 key 從 storage 裡刪除。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"storage.clear_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Storage/clear\"><code>Storage.clear()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>執行此方法，會刪除所有在 storage 裡的 key。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"範例","title":"範例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>在這裡，我們藉由呼叫 <code>localStorage</code> 來存取 <code>Storage</code> 物件，首先使用 <code>!localStorage.getItem('bgcolor')</code> 來確認 storage 裡是否有項目存在。</p>\n<p>如果有，則執行函示 <code>setStyles()</code> ，這個函示使用 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Storage/getItem\"><code>Storage.getItem()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 取得 storage 的值，並且用這些值更新頁面樣式 。</p>\n<p>如果沒有，便執行另一個函示 <code>populateStorage()</code>，他使用 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Storage/setItem\"><code>Storage.setItem()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 先設定 storage 項目的值，然後才執行<code>setStyles()</code>。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span>localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'bgcolor'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">populateStorage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">setStyles</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">populateStorage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'bgcolor'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'bgcolor'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'font'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'font'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'image'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'image'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">setStyles</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> currentColor <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'bgcolor'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> currentFont <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'font'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> currentImage <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'image'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'bgcolor'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> currentColor<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'font'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> currentFont<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'image'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> currentImage<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  htmlElem<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>backgroundColor <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'#'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> currentColor<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  pElem<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>fontFamily <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> currentFont<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  imgElem<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setAttribute</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'src'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> currentImage<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>備註：</strong> 想要看這個範例完整運行，可以參考我們的 <a href=\"https://mdn.github.io/dom-examples/web-storage/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Storage Demo</a>.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"規範","id":"規範","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webstorage.html#storage","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.Storage"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"瀏覽器相容性","id":"瀏覽器相容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.Storage","dataURL":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Storage/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Storage_API/Using_the_Web_Storage_API\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Using the Web Storage API (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Window/localStorage\"><code>Window.localStorage</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Window/sessionStorage\"><code>Window.sessionStorage</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CacheStorage\"><code>CacheStorage</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"屬性","id":"屬性"},{"text":"方法","id":"方法"},{"text":"範例","id":"範例"},{"text":"規範","id":"規範"},{"text":"瀏覽器相容性","id":"瀏覽器相容性"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Web Storage API (en-US) 中的 Storage 介面提供了存取特定 domain session 及本機儲存的方法。舉例而言，它能夠對存取的資料進行新增、刪除、修改，","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Storage","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Almacenamiento","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Storage","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Storage","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Storage","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Storage","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Storage","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Storage","locale"